Notes on data and disclosure:

This project consumes data from Upstox, Yahoo Finance, NSE archives, and
Perplexity Sonar. Each of those services has its own terms of use governing
how their data may be redistributed; the MIT licence above applies to the
GammaLeak source code only, not to any data products fetched at runtime.

The signal-derivation logic in this repository is provided for educational,
research, and portfolio-review purposes. It is not investment advice and is
not a trading system — there is no order-execution layer. Use at your own
risk.
